    emp=employee_details.query.filter_by(email=email).first() #filter and get whole details
    if not emp:
        return jsonify({}), 404
    return jsonify(emp_schema.dump(emp))
```

You can get your employee by entering `/getemp?email=&lt;your employee email&gt;`

